    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Tip: This is to warm your tortillas \u2013 alternatively, add them to a plate and pop in the microwave!</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>pepper & red onion </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 3-4 min until starting to soften</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-beef-fajitas-with-yoghurt/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>seeded tortillas</strong> to 1 <span class=\"text-danger\">[2] </span>baking tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 2-3 min or until they're warmed through (alternatively, add the tortillas to a plate and microwave for 1-2 min!)</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-beef-fajitas-with-yoghurt/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the veg has softened, add the <strong>smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> ground cumin</strong>, <strong>beef strips</strong> and <strong>soy sauce</strong></p><p>Add a grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and sear for 1-2 min, this will prevent the beef strips from overcooking \u2013 this is your <strong>smoky beef fajita filling</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-beef-fajitas-with-yoghurt/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Wash, then tear the <strong>little gem lettuce</strong> into rough pieces</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-beef-fajitas-with-yoghurt/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Fill each <strong>warmed tortilla </strong>with the <strong>torn little gem lettuce </strong>and<strong> smoky beef fajita filling</strong></p><p>Dollop over the <strong>natural yoghurt</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 5
        }
    ],
